    <entry>
      <title>Hexo Butterfly主题常用的标签外挂</title>
      <link href="/posts/4a17b156.html"/>
      <url>/posts/4a17b156.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="label-标签"><a href="#label-标签" class="headerlink" title="label-标签"></a>label-标签</h2><p>语法如下：颜色值仅支持：<mark class="hl-label default">default</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label blue">blue</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label pink">pink</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label red">red</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label purple">purple</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label orange">orange</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label green">green</mark>  。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% label text color %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>举例：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% label 先帝 %&#125;创业未半，而&#123;% label 中道崩殂 blue %&#125;。今天下三分，&#123;% label 益州疲敝 pink %&#125;，此诚&#123;% label 危急存亡之秋 red %&#125;也！</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><mark class="hl-label default">先帝</mark> 创业未半，而<mark class="hl-label blue">中道崩殂</mark> 。今天下三分，<mark class="hl-label pink">益州疲敝</mark> ，此诚<mark class="hl-label red">危急存亡之秋</mark> 也！<h2 id="button-按钮"><a href="#button-按钮" class="headerlink" title="button-按钮"></a>button-按钮</h2><p>语法为：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% btn [url],[text],[icon],[color] [style] [layout] [position] [size] %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>各个参数含义：可选参数可留空。</p><table><thead><tr><th>参数</th><th>含义</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>url</code></td><td>链接。</td></tr><tr><td><code>text</code></td><td>按钮上的文字内容</td></tr><tr><td><code>icon</code></td><td>【可选】，按钮上的图标，位于文字前面</td></tr><tr><td><code>color</code></td><td>【可选】，颜色，颜色值同样是上述7种。下面的style留空时，则为背景色；style为outline:字体与边框颜色</td></tr><tr><td><code>style</code></td><td>【可选】，属性值：留空/outline</td></tr><tr><td><code>layout</code></td><td>【可选】，属性值：留空/block</td></tr><tr><td><code>position</code></td><td>【可选】，按钮位置，默认留空为left，若上述layout设置为block，则可设置为center或right</td></tr><tr><td><code>size</code></td><td>【可选】，按钮大小，可选值：留空/larger</td></tr></tbody></table><p>举例：前三项最好加上逗号分隔，后面可以用空格来分隔，且顺序随意。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% btn &#x27;https://lovewhoilove.gitee.io/posts/4a17b156&#x27; ,本文地址,far fa-hand-point-right,outline green larger %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：可以点击查看效果。</p><a class="btn-beautify outline green larger" href="https://lovewhoilove.gitee.io/posts/4a17b156"   title="本文地址"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>本文地址</span></a><h2 id="note"><a href="#note" class="headerlink" title="note"></a>note</h2><p>以我的经验来看，note 可用于<strong>批注</strong>、<strong>注意项</strong>或<strong>引文</strong>。</p><h3 id="一般用法"><a href="#一般用法" class="headerlink" title="一般用法"></a>一般用法</h3><p>语法如下所示：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note [class] [no-icon] [style] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Any content (support inline tags too.io).</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>各个参数含义如下表所示：</p><table><thead><tr><th>名称</th><th>用法</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>class</code></td><td>【可选】，可选值有：<code>default</code> / <code>primary</code> / <code>success</code> / <code>info</code> / <code>warning</code> / <code>danger</code>，各个标识代表不同颜色，印象中在Bootstrap中用过</td></tr><tr><td><code>no-icon</code></td><td>【可选】，表示不显示 icon，显然直接不配置即可。</td></tr><tr><td><code>style</code></td><td>【可选】，可选值有：<code>simple</code> / <code>modern</code> / <code>flat</code> / <code>disabled</code>，可覆盖配置文件中的设置。</td></tr></tbody></table><p>默认样式是主题配置文件配置的属性（我这里配置的simple），<strong>这里指定的值可以覆盖配置文件中的设置</strong>。</p><ol><li><p>最简单的写法如下：</p> <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">默认 提示块标签</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 效果：若要去除前面的空白，则参看最后一种写法，加上<code>no-icon</code>属性。</p> <div class="note simple"><p>默认 提示块标签</p></div></li><li><p>default风格</p> <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note default %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">default 提示块标签</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 效果：后面依此类推</p> <div class="note default simple"><p>default 提示块标签</p></div></li><li><p>primary风格</p> <div class="note primary simple"><p>primary 提示块标签</p></div></li><li><p>success风格</p> <div class="note success simple"><p>success 提示块标签</p></div></li><li><p>info风格</p> <div class="note info simple"><p>info 提示块标签</p></div></li><li><p>warning风格</p> <div class="note warning simple"><p>warning 提示块标签</p></div></li><li><p>danger风格</p> <div class="note danger simple"><p>danger 提示块标签</p></div></li><li><p>若上述风格的第三个参数设置为disabled，写法如下：</p> <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note success disabled%&#125;</span><br><span class="line">success  disabled</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 效果如下：则会失去<strong>外边框的装饰</strong>，其余风格依此类推，这里不再赘述。</p> <div class="note success disabled"><p>success  disabled</p></div></li><li><p>若设置了<code>no-icon</code>属性</p> <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note success no-icon%&#125;</span><br><span class="line">success  disabled</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 效果为：</p> <div class="note success no-icon simple"><p>success  no-icon</p></div><p> 额外地，我们再来看另外两种风格：</p> <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note success modern%&#125;</span><br><span class="line">success  no-icon</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% note success flat%&#125;</span><br><span class="line">success  no-icon</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 效果分别如下：这里将四种风格分别罗列，方便对比。</p> <div class="note success simple"><p>success  simple</p></div> <div class="note success modern"><p>success  modern</p></div> <div class="note success flat"><p>success  flat</p></div> <div class="note success disabled"><p>success  disabled</p></div></li></ol><h3 id="自定义icon"><a href="#自定义icon" class="headerlink" title="自定义icon"></a>自定义icon</h3><p>在上述基础用法基础上，再来看一种高级写法：可以自定义颜色，而且可以自定义图标。</p><div class="note orange no-icon flat"><p><strong>注意事项</strong>：</p><ol><li><p>这里可选颜色值也仅支持：<mark class="hl-label default">default</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label blue">blue</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label pink">pink</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label red">red</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label purple">purple</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label orange">orange</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label green">green</mark>  ；</p></li><li><p>由于butterfly主题引入了<a href="https://fontawesome.com/">Font Awesome</a>图标，其余图标库则还需引入主题才能使用（例如阿里的<a href="https://www.iconfont.cn/">iconfont</a>，后面有时间可以专门出一篇博客来讲讲）。</p></li><li><p>这里若要用simple风格，则不能省略simple参数，这里要和上面区分开。</p></li></ol></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note [color] [icon] [style] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Any content (support inline tags too.io).</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们已经了解了simple、modern以及flat风格了，下面我们就以simple风格为例来介绍。</p><p>这里我们以喇叭图标为例：font awesome中改图标的属性值为：<code>fas fa-bullhorn</code>，例如蓝色的喇叭风格：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note blue &#x27;fas fa-bullhorn&#x27; simple %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">blue 喇叭 simple</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><div class="note blue icon-padding simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>blue 喇叭 simple</p></div><p>我们再加入一些动画效果，例如：</p><ul><li><p><strong>心跳</strong>（即有节拍的放大缩写）：图标属性后面加上<code>fa-beat</code>即可：</p>  <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note blue &#x27;fas fa-bullhorn fa-beat&#x27; simple %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">blue 喇叭 simple 心跳</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  效果为：</p>  <div class="note blue icon-padding simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn fa-beat"></i><p>blue 喇叭 simple 心跳</p></div></li></ul><p>此外，还有：</p><ul><li><p><strong>淡入淡出</strong>：<code>fas fa-bullhorn fa-fade</code></p><div class="note blue icon-padding simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn fa-fade"></i><p>blue 喇叭 simple 淡入淡出</p></div></li><li><p><strong>心跳叠加淡入淡出</strong>：<code>fas fa-bullhorn fa-beat-fade</code></p><div class="note blue icon-padding simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn fa-beat-fade"></i><p>blue 喇叭 simple 心跳叠加淡入淡出</p></div></li><li><p><strong>上下弹跳</strong>：<code>fas fa-bullhorn fa-bounce</code></p><div class="note blue icon-padding simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn fa-bounce"></i><p>blue 喇叭 simple 上下弹跳</p></div></li><li><p><strong>三维旋转</strong>：默认绕<code>y</code>轴旋转,<code>fas fa-bullhorn fa-flip</code></p><div class="note blue icon-padding simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn fa-flip"></i><p>blue 喇叭 simple 三维旋转</p></div></li><li><p><strong>来回摇动</strong>：<code>fas fa-bullhorn fa-shake</code></p><div class="note blue icon-padding simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn fa-shake"></i><p>blue 喇叭 simple 来回摇动</p></div></li><li><p><strong>旋转</strong>：默认是顺时针，<code>fas fa-bullhorn fa-spin</code></p><div class="note blue icon-padding simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn fa-spin"></i><p>blue 喇叭 simple  旋转</p></div></li></ul><div class="note info flat"><p>有关动画更详细的用法，更多参数、样式的设置，详见<a href="https://fontawesome.com/docs/web/style/animate">FontAwesome官方文档</a>👈。</p></div><h2 id="taghide-隐藏标记"><a href="#taghide-隐藏标记" class="headerlink" title="taghide-隐藏标记"></a>taghide-隐藏标记</h2><h3 id="hideInline-内联"><a href="#hideInline-内联" class="headerlink" title="hideInline-内联"></a>hideInline-内联</h3><p>语法为：<strong>这里的颜色值没有限制</strong>，可以用十六进制的任意值。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% hideInline content,display,bg,color %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p><code>content</code>： 文本内容</p></li><li><p><code>display</code>:：按钮显示的文字(<strong>可选</strong>)</p></li><li><p><code>bg</code>：按钮的背景颜色(<strong>可选</strong>)</p></li><li><p><code>color</code>:：按钮文字的颜色(<strong>可选</strong>)</p></li></ul><p>举例：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">门里站着一个人? &#123;% hideInline 闪,#FF7242,#fff %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果为：</p><p>门里站着一个人? <span class="hide-inline"><button type="button" class="hide-button" style="background-color: #FF7242;color: #fff">查看答案  </button><span class="hide-content">闪 </span></span></p><h3 id="hideBlock-块级"><a href="#hideBlock-块级" class="headerlink" title="hideBlock-块级"></a>hideBlock-块级</h3><p>语法为：和上面的语法类似</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% hideBlock display,bg,color %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">content</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endhideBlock %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>举例：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">门里站着一个人?</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% hideBlock 查看答案,#FF7242,#fff %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">闪</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endhideBlock %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果为：</p><p>门里站着一个人?</p><div class="hide-block"><button type="button" class="hide-button" style="background-color: #FF7242;color: #fff">查看答案    </button><div class="hide-content"><p>闪</p></div></div><h3 id="hideToggle-切换"><a href="#hideToggle-切换" class="headerlink" title="hideToggle-切换"></a>hideToggle-切换</h3><p>语法同上，只不过标签名改为hideToggle，适用场景：<strong>展示的内容有很多，想暂时隐藏在收缩框里，需要看时再展开。</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% hideToggle display,bg,color %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">content</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endhideToggle %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>举例：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% hideToggle 教程详细内容,#49b1f5,#fff %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">content</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endhideToggle %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果为：</p><details class="toggle" style="border: 1px solid #49b1f5"><summary class="toggle-button" style="background-color: #49b1f5;color: #fff">教程详细内容</summary><div class="toggle-content"><p>content<br>…<br>…<br>…<br>…</p></div></details><h2 id="mermaid"><a href="#mermaid" class="headerlink" title="mermaid"></a>mermaid</h2><p>适用mermaid标签可以绘制：flowchart（流程图）、sequence diagram（时序图）、class diagram（类别图）、state diagram（状态图）、gantt（甘特图）及pie chart（饼状图），详情可以查看<a href="https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/">官方文档</a>👈，这里不再举例说明。</p><p>使用此功能需要修改主题以下配置：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">mermaid:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">theme:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">light:</span> <span class="string">default</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">dark:</span> <span class="string">dark</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="tabs-多标签"><a href="#tabs-多标签" class="headerlink" title="tabs-多标签"></a>tabs-多标签</h2><p>语法为：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% tabs Unique name, [index] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab [Tab caption] [@icon] --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Any content (support inline tags too).</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endtabs %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th>参数</th><th>含义</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>Unique name</code></td><td>Tab块的唯一名称，名称唯一即可，具体含义不用了解很清楚🤔。</td></tr><tr><td><code>index</code></td><td>选定的选项卡的索引号。若<code>不指定</code>，则默认选择第一个选项卡；若<code>指定为-1</code>，则不会选择任何选项卡。</td></tr><tr><td><code>Tab caption</code></td><td>当前选项卡的标题。若<code>不指定</code>，则会使用带有制表符索引后缀的唯一名称作为标题；若<code>未指定标题，但指定了图标</code>，则标题将为空。</td></tr><tr><td><code>@icon</code></td><td>Font Awesome的图标全名，</td></tr></tbody></table><p>举例：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% tabs test, 3 %&#125; # 默认选中第3个标签</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**This is Tab 1.**</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab @fas fa-bullhorn fa-shake--&gt; # 带有icon</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**This is Tab 2.**</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab 炸弹@fas fa-bomb--&gt; #带有icon并配有文字</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**This is Tab 3.**</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endtabs %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="tabs" id="test"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#test-1">test 1</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#test-2"><i class="fas fa-bullhorn fa-shake" style="text-align: center;"></i></button></li><li class="tab active"><button type="button" data-href="#test-3"><i class="fas fa-bomb fa-beat-fade"></i>炸弹</button></li></ul><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content" id="test-1"><p><strong>This is Tab 1.</strong></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="test-2"><p><strong>This is Tab 2.</strong></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content active" id="test-3"><p><strong>This is Tab 3.</strong></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div></div><h2 id="inlineImg-内联图片"><a href="#inlineImg-内联图片" class="headerlink" title="inlineImg-内联图片"></a>inlineImg-内联图片</h2><p>我们默认使用的<code>![]()</code>Markdown语法默认是块级元素，即独占一行，若以内联元素显示图片，可以使用<code>inlineImg</code>这个标签，语法如下：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% inlineImg [src] [height] %&#125; # src：图片地址；height：显示高度</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>举例：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">本文封面图：&#123;% inlineImg https://u-1303826255.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202212221538548.jpg 50px %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><p>封面图：<img class="inline-img" src="https://u-1303826255.cos.ap-nanjing.myqcloud.com/202212221538548.jpg?imageMogr2/quality/75/format/webp/interlace/0" style="height:50px"/></p><h2 id="timeline-时间线"><a href="#timeline-时间线" class="headerlink" title="timeline-时间线"></a>timeline-时间线</h2><p>语法如下：显然，最外层标签定义总的title和整体的color属性，颜色值仅支持：<mark class="hl-label default">default</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label blue">blue</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label pink">pink</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label red">red</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label purple">purple</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label orange">orange</mark>  / <mark class="hl-label green">green</mark>  。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% timeline title,color %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- timeline title 1 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">content 1</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtimeline --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- timeline title 2--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">content 2</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtimeline --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#...</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- timeline title n--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">content n</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtimeline --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endtimeline %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>举例：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% timeline 2022 ,blue %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- timeline 12-01 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">测试内容1</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtimeline --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- timeline 12-03--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">测试内容2</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtimeline --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#...</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- timeline title n--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">测试内容n</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtimeline --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endtimeline %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><div class="timeline undefined"><div class='timeline-item headline'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2022 blue</p></div></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>12-01</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>测试内容1</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>12-03</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>测试内容2</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>title n</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>测试内容n</p></div></div></div>]]></content>
      
      
